{
  "texts": [
    "To introduce SFA in spiking neural networks, a neuron model can be used which includes an adaptive threshold property 28.",
    "SSNs with these kinds of neurons learn quickly, even without synaptic plasticity 29.",
    "Moreover, SFA helps in attaining higher computational efficiency in SNNs 17.",
    "For example, to achieve a store-and-recall cycle (working memory) of duration 1200 ms, a single exponential adaptive model requires a decay constant, τ a = 1200 ms in ref.",
    "17, while a double exponential adaptive threshold model requires decay constants of τ a1 = 30 ms and τ a2 = 300 ms 19 -the latter being more efficient and sophisticated with four adaptation parameters compared to two parameters in ref."
  ]
}